Class Review

java.lang.Object
  pa07.Review

public class Review
extends java.lang.Object

A Review has four components.

  • the user making the review
  • the movie being reviewed
  • the rating (an integer from 0 to 5)
  • the timestamp of the review (number of seconds in 1/1/1970)

Constructor Summary

          A review is created by specifying a userId, a movieId, a rating, and a timestamp indicating the number of seconds since 1/1/70.
